OL,3,CCouncil tax to rise by maximum amount
OL,4,Cin nearly all areas, research says
OL,6,FNearly all councils plan to raise
OL,7,Ftheir taxes by the biggest amount they
OL,8,Fare allowed to without having to hold
OL,9,Fa local referendum.
OL,11,FOf the 136 authorities which have
OL,12,Fdeclared their proposals, 128 (94%)
OL,13,Fare looking to increase bills in April
OL,14,Fby 4.99%.
OL,16,FSam Corcoran, Labour leader of
OL,17,FCheshire East Council and CCN vice-
OL,18,Fchairman, said councils have to make
OL,19,F"some of their toughest decisions"
OL,20,Fbecause of increased costs and spikes
OL,21,Fin demand for social care services.
