OL,6,FThese councils, a mix of county and
OL,7,Funitary authorities, are said to be
OL,8,Fstill facing a collective funding gap
OL,9,Fof #1.1 billion over the next two
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FMr Corcoran said, while the additional
OL,13,Ffunding provided by the government
OL,14,Fwould make a tangible difference and
OL,15,Fprotect services, the fragile state of
OL,16,Fcouncil finances means council tax
OL,17,Fbills had to rise to ensure
OL,18,Fsustainability.
